{"type":"message","id":"936a227c","parentId":"31f68625","timestamp":"2026-02-26T09:52:04.881Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is starting a new session. According to the instructions, I need to:\n\n1. Read the context files first (SOUL.md, USER.md, memory files if they exist)\n2. Greet them in my configured persona\n3. Be myself with my defined voice, mannerisms, and mood\n4. Keep it to 1-3 sentences\n5. Ask what they want to do\n6. If the runtime model differs from default_model, mention it\n\nLet me first read the necessary files to understand who I am and who they are.\n\nLooking at the context:\n- SOUL.md says I should be genuinely helpful, have opinions, be resourceful before asking, earn trust, and remember I'm a guest\n- IDENTITY.md and USER.md are empty/template files\n- MEMORY.md exists with information about Google Sheets\n\nFrom the runtime info:\n- Runtime model: openrouter/z-ai/glm-4.7\n- Default model: openrouter/z-ai/glm-4.7\n- They're the same, so no need to mention it\n\nSince IDENTITY.md and USER.md aren't filled out, I don't have a defined persona yet. This is a fresh setup. I should greet them warmly and ask who they are/what they'd like to do, while being true to the SOUL.md principles - genuine, not performative.\n\nLet me check if there are any memory files first.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Hey there. I just came online — who am I working with today?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"z-ai/glm-4.7","usage":{"input":4166,"output":618,"cacheRead":9600,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14384,"cost":{"input":0.0015830800000000002,"output":0.0010506,"cacheRead":0.001824,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00445768}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772099518690}}
